---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="ABOUT | SYNCODE"
    description="SYNCODE Identity & Strategy. 30年のディレクション経験とAIの演算能力を同期させ、ブランドの本質を抽出するクリエイティブ・プロトコルについて。"
>
    <style>
        .about-layout {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 100px 5% 80px;
            color: var(--color-text);
            line-height: 2.2;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .about-section {
            margin-bottom: 120px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 700px; /* テキスト部分は読みやすさのため700px程度に制限 */
        }

        .about-section:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0px;
        }

        .about-section h2 { 
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 800; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            letter-spacing: 0.4em;
            color: #ccc; 
            margin: 0 0 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .about-section p { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            word-break: keep-all; 
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .about-section p span {
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .spacer {
            display: block;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .about-section strong span {
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: block;
            color: #000;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }

        /* Proof to Action (Bridge Section) */
        .bridge-section {
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 120px 80px;
            background: #fdfdfd;
            border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            text-align: center;
            /* 初期状態：隠しておく */
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), 
                        transform 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        /* 出現時 */
        .bridge-section.is-visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .bridge-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.4em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .bridge-title {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #000;
        }

        .bridge-desc {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
        }

        .btn-works {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 24px 60px;
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .btn-works:hover {
            background: #333;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            letter-spacing: 0.25em; /* わずかに広がる演出 */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-layout {
                padding: 60px 20px 80px;
            }
            .about-section {
                margin-bottom: 80px;
            }
            .about-section strong span {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .bridge-section {
                padding: 60px 30px;
                margin-top: 40px;
            }
            .bridge-title {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
            .btn-works {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>

    <div class="about-layout">
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Identity</h2>
            <p>
                <span>孝森 弘章 / Hiroaki Takamori</span>
                <span class="spacer"></span>
                <span>AI Creative Director / Brand Director</span>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Method</h2>
            <p>
                <span>Logic & Intuition</span>
                <span class="spacer"></span>
                <span>Experience & AI Acceleration</span>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>History</h2>
            <p>
                <strong><span>30 Years of Insight. Synchronized with AI.</span></strong>
                <span>デザイン黎明期から現在に至るまで、</span><br>
                <span>30年にわたりブランドの核心を射抜く</span><br>
                <span>ディレクションを積み重ねてきました。</span>
                <span class="spacer"></span>
                <span>蓄積された審美眼とAIの演算能力を同期させ、</span><br>
                <span>時代に流されない本質的な価値を構築します。</span>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Strategy</h2>
            <p>
                <strong><span>Minimalist Logic. Maximum Impact.</span></strong>
                <span>不要な要素を削ぎ落とし、ブランドが持つ</span><br>
                <span>「真の記号（SYNCODE）」を抽出すること。</span>
                <span class="spacer"></span>
                <span>熟練の直感による「判断」と、AIによる</span><br>
                <span>「具現化」を高度に同期させ、ビジネスに</span><br>
                <span>静かな、しかし確かな熱量をもたらします。</span>
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- BRIDGE TO WORKS -->
        <div class="bridge-section">
            <span class="bridge-label">Identity in Action</span>
            <h2 class="bridge-title">実証：概念を形へ</h2>
            <p class="bridge-desc">
                思想を数式のように精緻に積み上げ、確かな実績へと変換する。<br/>
                SYNCODEが手がけたプロジェクトの実例をご覧ください。
            </p>
            <a href="/works/" class="btn-works">VIEW WORKS →</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const observerOptions = {
            root: null,
            rootMargin: '0px',
            threshold: 0.1
        };

        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
                }
            });
        }, observerOptions);

        const bridgeSection = document.querySelector('.bridge-section');
        if (bridgeSection) {
            observer.observe(bridgeSection);
        }
    </script>
</BaseLayout>